|-------|-------|-----|
| Gold | `#C9A84C` | Primary accent |
| Gold Light | `#E8D5A3` | Hover |
| Gold Dark | `#A07830` | Pressed |
| Black | `#111111` | Background |
| Black Soft | `#1E1E1E` | Cards |
| White | `#F9F9F9` | Text |
