Typography: Playfair Display (headings), Inter (body/UI). Radius: 6px / 12px / 20px. Grid: 3 cols desktop → 2 tablet → 1 mobile.

## API Integration

Base URL from `environment.apiUrl` (`/api`).

**Dishes:** `GET/POST /dishes`, `PUT/DELETE /dishes/:id` (write = admin)
**Packages:** `GET/POST /packages`, `PUT/DELETE /packages/:id` (write = admin)

Service pattern — inject `HttpClient`, use typed responses:

```typescript
@Injectable({ providedIn: 'root' })
export class DishService {
  private apiUrl = `${environment.apiUrl}/dishes`;
  getAll() { return this.http.get<Dish[]>(this.apiUrl); }
  create(dish: Partial<Dish>) { return this.http.post<Dish>(this.apiUrl, dish); }
  update(id: string, dish: Partial<Dish>) { return this.http.put<Dish>(`${this.apiUrl}/${id}`, dish); }
  delete(id: string) { return this.http.delete<void>(`${this.apiUrl}/${id}`); }
}
```

## Component Conventions

- Loading states: `isLoading = signal(false)` + shared `LoaderComponent`
- Lists: load in `ngOnInit`, render grid of card components
- Forms: validate before submit, disable submit while saving, emit `onSaved` after success
- Delete: confirm dialog before API call, reload list on success

## Feature Checklist

**Design system:** `_variables.scss`, `_typography.scss`, `styles.scss`, responsive grid, button states, card hover effects

**Dishes:** DishService, DishListComponent, DishCardComponent, DishDetailComponent (`/dishes/:id`), DishFormComponent (admin)

**Packages:** PackageService, PackageListComponent, PackageCardComponent, PackageDetailComponent (`/packages/:id`), PackageFormComponent (admin)

**Home:** Hero + Unsplash bg, featured dishes/packages carousels (first 3 from API), CTAs

**Admin:** Sidebar (Manage Dishes/Packages), content area for forms, route `/admin/dashboard` (admin guard)

**Shared:** LoaderComponent — gold spinning ring on all API calls

